Subject: FSAA job not completed
Description: It appears that one of my fsaa scans failed and thinks it is running. Also the bulk import is running and will soon get to this server. Need help ensuring the job ended and if need be delete the tier2 databases so the next scan will run
What_We_Know__c: Had call with customer today for another issue and looked at this. Analysis Task "update stats" was failing on his bulk import. Disabled this and Customer will run again and give update tomorrow.
Next_Steps__c: Customer to rerun job with Analysis disabled and give results tomorrow.
Solution_Comment__c: Disabling the "statistics" analysis task on the bulk import allowed the scans to fully complete.
